<ab>Herczog <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Beyern</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> vormals
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von etlicher <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> wegen, den das ir in
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> stat czu Landshute bekümert ist
                                <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>, darümb
                            <expan>sende<ex>n</ex></expan> wir czu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Krag<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add>und</add> Hansen <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> davon czu <expan>rede<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc. ut in
                            <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ii post
                        <expan>Margar<ex>ete</ex></expan>.</ab>
